<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Painel de Reembolso & Chargeback — Maio/Junho 2026</title>
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');

:root {
  --sidebar-bg: #0f2e2c;
  --sidebar-bg-2: #143a37;
  --sidebar-text: #a8c4c1;
  --sidebar-text-dim: #6b8c89;

  --page-bg: #f3f5f4;
  --card-bg: #ffffff;
  --card-bg-2: #f6f8f7;
  --border: #e8ece9;
  --border-strong: #d8e0dc;

  --text: #15201d;
  --text-dim: #6b756f;
  --text-faint: #99a39d;

  --accent: #0f9c8f;
  --accent-soft: #e3f6f3;
  --amber: #e8943c;
  --amber-soft: #fdf1e3;
  --red: #e2554a;
  --red-soft: #fdebe9;
  --green: #2da86f;
  --green-soft: #e7f6ee;

  --grad-1: #0f9c8f;
  --grad-2: #14b8a6;

  --font: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
  --mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  --radius: 16px;
  --shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(15,32,29,0.04), 0 8px 24px rgba(15,32,29,0.04);
}

* { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
body { font-family: var(--font); background: var(--page-bg); color: var(--text); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }

.app { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr; min-height: 100vh; }

/* SIDEBAR */
.sidebar { background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--sidebar-bg) 0%, var(--sidebar-bg-2) 100%); padding: 24px 16px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; position: sticky; top: 0; height: 100vh; }
.sidebar-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 0 8px 24px; color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 16.5px; }
.sidebar-logo .mark { width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 9px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--grad-1), var(--grad-2)); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; flex-shrink: 0; }
.nav-section-label { font-size: 10.5px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--sidebar-text-dim); padding: 14px 12px 8px; font-weight: 600; }
.nav-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 11px; padding: 10px 12px; border-radius: 10px; color: var(--sidebar-text); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; margin-bottom: 2px; transition: background .15s, color .15s; text-decoration: none; border: none; background: none; width: 100%; text-align: left; font-family: var(--font); }
.nav-item:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); color: #fff; }
.nav-item.active { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--grad-1), var(--grad-2)); color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(15,156,143,0.35); }
.nav-item .ico { width: 17px; height: 17px; flex-shrink: 0; opacity: 0.9; }
.nav-item.active .ico { opacity: 1; }
.sidebar-footer { margin-top: auto; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
.sidebar-status { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 10px 12px; font-size: 11.5px; color: var(--sidebar-text-dim); }
.sidebar-status .dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--accent); flex-shrink:0; }

/* MAIN */
.main { padding: 28px 32px 60px; max-width: 1320px; }
.topbar { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 26px; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px; }
.greeting h1 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
.greeting p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-top: 3px; }
.topbar-actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
.period-pill { background: var(--card-bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 8px 14px; border-radius: 11px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); font-weight: 500; font-family: var(--mono); }

/* KPI */
.kpi-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(190px, 1fr)); gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 22px; }
.kpi { background: var(--card-bg); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 18px 20px; box-shadow: var(--shadow); }
.kpi-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.kpi-value { font-family: var(--font); font-size: 23px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
.kpi-delta { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; margin-top: 9px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 7px; font-weight: 700; }
.kpi-delta.up { background: var(--green-soft); color: var(--green); }
.kpi-delta.down { background: var(--red-soft); color: var(--red); }
.kpi-delta.flat { background: var(--card-bg-2); color: var(--text-faint); }

/* PANELS */
.panel { background: var(--card-bg); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 22px 24px; margin-bottom: 18px; box-shadow: var(--shadow); }
.panel-head { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; margin-bottom: 18px; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; }
.panel-title { font-size: 15.5px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); }
.panel-sub { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11.5px; color: var(--text-faint); }

.grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr; gap: 18px; }
.grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 18px; }
@media (max-width: 1100px) { .grid-2, .grid-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .app { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .sidebar { display:none; } }

svg.chart { width: 100%; height: auto; overflow: visible; }
.axis-label { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; fill: var(--text-faint); }
.grid-line { stroke: var(--border); stroke-width: 1; }
.chart-line { fill: none; stroke-width: 2.5; }
.chart-dot { stroke-width: 0; }
.chart-area { opacity: 0.12; }

table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 12px; }
th { text-align: left; padding: 9px 10px; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-faint); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-strong); cursor: pointer; user-select: none; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: 700; }
th:hover { color: var(--accent); }
th.num, td.num { text-align: right; }
td { padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text); white-space: nowrap; }
tr:hover td { background: var(--card-bg-2); }

.pill { display: inline-block; padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 7px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
.pill-black100 { background: var(--red-soft); color: var(--red); }
.pill-black70 { background: var(--amber-soft); color: var(--amber); }
.pill-black50 { background: var(--accent-soft); color: var(--accent); }
.pill-nd { background: var(--card-bg-2); color: var(--text-faint); }

.legend { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); }
.legend-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
.legend-swatch { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 3px; }

.callout { background: var(--red-soft); border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px 16px; font-size: 12.5px; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--text-dim); margin-top: 12px; border: none; }
.callout b { color: var(--text); }
.callout.warn { background: var(--amber-soft); }
.callout.ok { background: var(--green-soft); }

.foot { margin-top: 32px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10.5px; color: var(--text-faint); line-height: 1.7; }
.scroll-x { overflow-x: auto; }

.status-tag { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 700; white-space: nowrap; }
.status-alert { background: var(--red-soft); color: var(--red); }
.status-watch { background: var(--amber-soft); color: var(--amber); }
.status-ok { background: var(--green-soft); color: var(--green); }
.status-nd { background: var(--card-bg-2); color: var(--text-faint); }

select { background: var(--card-bg); color: var(--text); border: 1px solid var(--border-strong); border-radius: 9px; padding: 8px 13px; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 12px; }

.subgrid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; margin-top: 4px; }
@media (max-width: 1100px) { .subgrid-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
.subpanel { background: var(--card-bg-2); border-radius: 13px; padding: 15px 17px; }
.subpanel-title { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; color: var(--text-faint); margin-bottom: 11px; font-weight: 700; }
.bar-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 7px; font-size: 11px; }
.bar-row .label { width: 92px; flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--text-dim); font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10.5px; }
.bar-row .track { flex: 1; background: var(--border); border-radius: 4px; height: 13px; overflow: hidden; }
.bar-row .fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 4px; }
.bar-row .val { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10.5px; color: var(--text); width: 36px; text-align: right; flex-shrink:0; font-weight: 600; }

.reason-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 8px; padding: 6px 0; font-size: 11.5px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
.reason-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.reason-row .reason-text { color: var(--text-dim); flex: 1; }
.reason-row .reason-count { font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--text); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; }

.toggle-group { display: flex; gap: 4px; background: var(--card-bg-2); border-radius: 9px; padding: 3px; }
.toggle-btn { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; padding: 7px 13px; border-radius: 7px; border: none; background: none; color: var(--text-faint); cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; }
.toggle-btn.active { background: var(--card-bg); color: var(--accent); box-shadow: var(--shadow); }

::-webkit-scrollbar { height: 8px; width: 8px; }
::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--card-bg-2); }
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--border-strong); border-radius: 4px; }

.tooltip { position: fixed; background: #15201d; color: #fff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 8px 11px; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; pointer-events: none; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.1s; z-index: 50; white-space: nowrap; box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); }

.view { display: none; }
.view.active { display: block; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="app">

  <aside class="sidebar">
    <div class="sidebar-logo">
      <div class="mark">RF</div>
      RefundOps
    </div>
    <div class="nav-section-label">Painel</div>
    <button class="nav-item active" data-view="overview"><svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 3v18h18"/></svg>Visão geral</button>
    <button class="nav-item" data-view="evolution"><svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 3v18h18M7 14l4-4 3 3 5-6"/></svg>Evolução semanal</button>
    <button class="nav-item" data-view="products"><svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22a9 9 0 100-18 9 9 0 000 18zM12 7v5l3 2"/></svg>Produtos & black%</button>
    <button class="nav-item" data-view="affiliates"><svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 8a3.5 3.5 0 110 7 3.5 3.5 0 010-7zM3 20c0-3.5 2.7-6 6-6s6 2.5 6 6M17 8a2.5 2.5 0 110 5M21 20c0-2.8-1.6-5-4-5.7"/></svg>Afiliados</button>
    <button class="nav-item" data-view="profitability"><svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v20M2 12h20"/></svg>Lucratividade & black</button>
    <button class="nav-item" data-view="retention"><svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 12h4l3 8 4-16 3 8h4"/></svg>Retenção dia 0-1</button>
    <button class="nav-item" data-view="risk"><svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 9v4M12 17h.01M10.3 3.2a2 2 0 013.4 0l8.5 14.7a2 2 0 01-1.7 3H3.5a2 2 0 01-1.7-3z"/></svg>Risco & status</button>

    <button class="nav-item" data-view="affalerts"><svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10.3 3.2a2 2 0 013.4 0l8.5 14.7a2 2 0 01-1.7 3H3.5a2 2 0 01-1.7-3zM12 9v4M12 17h.01"/></svg>Afiliados em alerta</button>
    <button class="nav-item" data-view="lastweek"><svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 12h18M3 6h18M3 18h18"/></svg>Última semana</button>
    <div class="sidebar-footer">
      <div class="sidebar-status"><span class="dot"></span>Dados até 30/06/2026</div>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <main class="main">
    <div class="topbar">
      <div class="greeting">
        <h1 id="page-title">Visão geral</h1>
        <p id="page-subtitle">Evolução por produto, % black/upsell e afiliados — base 60 dias</p>
      </div>
      <div class="topbar-actions">
        <div class="period-pill">01 — 30 jun 2026</div>
      </div>
    </div>

  <div class="view active" id="view-overview">

    <div class="kpi-row" id="kpi-overview"></div>

    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="panel-head">
          <div class="panel-title">Faturamento × Refund% — Maio vs Junho</div>
          <div class="panel-sub">USD / %</div>
        </div>
        <div id="chart-overview-main"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="panel-head">
          <div class="panel-title">Net Profit &amp; Margem</div>
          <div class="panel-sub">USD / %</div>
        </div>
        <div id="chart-overview-margin"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <div class="panel-head">
        <div class="panel-title">Resumo por Período</div>
      </div>
      <div class="scroll-x"><table id="table-overview"></table></div>
    </div>
  
  </div>

  <div class="view" id="view-evolution">

    <div class="panel">
      <div class="panel-head">
        <div class="panel-title">Evolução Semanal de Junho — Faturamento &amp; Refund%</div>
        <div class="panel-sub">S1 a S4 + comparativo com Maio</div>
      </div>
      <div id="chart-weekly"></div>
      <div class="callout warn">
        <b>Atenção Semana 4 (22-30/06):</b> refund% salta para 22,3% (vs ~13% nas semanas 2 e 3), e net profit cai para 21,2% de margem — a pior da série. Vale investigar o que mudou nessa janela (campanhas, afiliados, ou alguma oferta específica).
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="panel-head"><div class="panel-title">Volume de Vendas por Semana</div></div>
        <div id="chart-weekly-volume"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="panel-head"><div class="panel-title">Net Profit por Semana</div></div>
        <div id="chart-weekly-profit"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <div class="panel-head">
        <div class="panel-title">Tabela Semanal Detalhada</div>
      </div>
      <div class="scroll-x"><table id="table-weekly"></table></div>
    </div>
  
  </div>

  <div class="view" id="view-products">

    <div class="panel">
      <div class="panel-head">
        <div class="panel-title">Refund% por Produto × % Black — Junho Completo</div>
        <div class="panel-sub">Ordenado por refund%, cor = intensidade black</div>
      </div>
      <div class="legend" style="margin-bottom:14px;">
        <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-swatch" style="background:var(--red)"></span>100% Black</div>
        <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-swatch" style="background:var(--amber)"></span>70% Black</div>
        <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-swatch" style="background:var(--accent)"></span>50% Black</div>
        <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-swatch" style="background:var(--text-faint)"></span>N/D</div>
      </div>
      <div id="chart-product-refund"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <div class="panel-head">
        <div class="panel-title">Evolução por Produto — Reembolso, Intervalo de Dias e Motivos</div>
        <select id="product-select"></select>
      </div>

      <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--text-faint);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:6px;">Faturamento (semanal)</div>
      <div id="chart-product-evolution-fat"></div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--text-faint);text-transform:uppercase;margin:14px 0 6px;">Refund % (semanal)</div>
      <div id="chart-product-evolution-refund"></div>

      <div style="margin-top:22px; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px;">
        <div class="panel-title" style="font-size:13px;">Detalhamento — base 60 dias (período total)</div>
        <div class="toggle-group" id="rf-cb-toggle">
          <button class="toggle-btn active" data-mode="refund">Reembolsos</button>
          <button class="toggle-btn" data-mode="chargeback">Chargebacks</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="subgrid-3" id="product-detail-grid">
        <div class="subpanel">
          <div class="subpanel-title">Intervalo até a solicitação</div>
          <div id="detail-bucket"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="subpanel">
          <div class="subpanel-title">Principais motivos</div>
          <div id="detail-reasons"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="subpanel">
          <div class="subpanel-title">Pedido principal vs upsell</div>
          <div id="detail-offertype"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <div class="panel-head">
        <div class="panel-title">Tabela Completa — Junho por Produto</div>
      </div>
      <div class="scroll-x"><table id="table-products"></table></div>
    </div>
  
  </div>

  <div class="view" id="view-affiliates">

    <div class="panel">
      <div class="panel-head">
        <div class="panel-title">Top Afiliados por Período</div>
        <select id="affiliate-period-select"></select>
      </div>
      <div class="scroll-x"><table id="table-affiliates"></table></div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <div class="panel-head">
        <div class="panel-title">% Refund dos Top Afiliados — Junho Completo</div>
      </div>
      <div id="chart-affiliate-refund"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <div class="panel-head">
        <div class="panel-title">Afiliados Master (90+ vendas) — Vendas, Refund e Chargeback</div>
        <div class="panel-sub">29 afiliados com 90+ pedidos somando todos os produtos · base "Master Affiliates"</div>
      </div>
      <div class="callout">
        <b>13 de 29</b> afiliados foram cruzados com dado individual real de Refund/Chargeback (base de Junho 1-18). Os demais 16 — em geral agências/call centers (FULL NEGOCIOS DIGITAIS, HelpGrid, TIGER OFFERS etc.) — não bateram por nome nessa base; a coluna "Taxa CB+Refund sobre Vendas" desses vem da planilha oficial de afiliados e é confiável mesmo sem o detalhamento individual.
      </div>
      <div class="scroll-x" style="margin-top:14px;"><table id="table-master90"></table></div>
    </div>
  
  </div>

  <div class="view" id="view-profitability">

    <div class="kpi-row" id="kpi-profitability"></div>

    <div class="panel">
      <div class="panel-head">
        <div class="panel-title">Vale a pena manter o Black? — Faturamento x Net Profit, Maio → Junho</div>
        <div class="panel-sub">Faturamento dobrou; lucro líquido não acompanhou na mesma proporção em vários produtos black</div>
      </div>
      <div id="chart-profit-growth"></div>
      <div class="callout warn">
        <b>Faturamento total cresceu 74% (maio→junho)</b>, mas o "excesso de reembolso" — comparando cada produto com o melhor desempenho da carteira (VigorLong, 10,2% de refund) — somou <b>$722.712 só em junho</b>, dos quais <b>99,8% vêm de produtos 70%+ black</b>. Esse valor seria lucro líquido adicional se a operação reduzisse o refund% ao nível do produto mais saudável da casa.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <div class="panel-head">
        <div class="panel-title">Simulação — BreathEaseX (maior produto da carteira, 100% black)</div>
        <div class="panel-sub">Faturamento atual: $2.446.820 · Refund atual: 29,5% ($722.763) · Net Profit atual: $579.198 (23,7% margem)</div>
      </div>
      <div id="chart-simulation"></div>
      <div class="callout ok">
        Reduzir o refund% do BreathEaseX para a faixa de 15-20% (ainda alto, mas mais controlado) liberaria entre <b>$233 mil e $356 mil</b> de net profit adicional por mês, sem precisar crescer faturamento — só reduzindo a "fuga" de receita pelo reembolso.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <div class="panel-head">
        <div class="panel-title">Excesso de Reembolso por Produto vs Baseline (10,2%)</div>
        <div class="panel-sub">Quanto cada produto perde de lucro líquido em excesso de refund, comparado ao melhor da carteira</div>
      </div>
      <div id="chart-excess-refund"></div>
